other.charge: 6.10 Weekday (Before 10:00), 3.10 Weekday (After 10:00), 3.10 Weekend and Bank Holiday. Weekly Pass 24.50.
other.description: Dagenham Dock Railway Station Car Park
Permits for parking here are not routinely granted, as they are for staff and contractors only, not even residents. Fines are regularly issued for those parking without a permit.
